  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Universal Health Coverage and Equity</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of this advocacy report is to reframe dialogues on Universal Health Coverage (UHC) so that equity is acknowledged as a central objective of UHC, an explicit consideration in any approach to achieve UHC, and an indicator for measuring progress towards UHC. It will make the investment case for addressing inequalities in health, draw on the evidence basis for how to do this, and seek to influence the post-2015 agenda.</narrative>
  </description>
